java.lang.Object

public class NervousSystemElementAgentStyle extends Object implements repast.simphony.visualization.visualization3D.style.Style3D<NervousSystemElement>
Defines the 3D style for Parkinson's model elements in the Repast simulation. This class implements Style3D to provide appearance, label, and transformation details for visualizing model elements.
